   and cytokine production.                                                     
 • Interferon-gamma (IFN-gamma): Explored for its role in immune activation and 
   potential therapeutic applications.                                          
 • Dexamethasone: A glucocorticoid used to modulate cytokine production and     
   inflammation.                                                                
 • Pentoxifylline: Investigated for its effects on TNF-alpha and IL-6 secretion.

